{"tid":672483,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］馬浚偉馬撚歷年新聞大集合！！！","createTime":"2018-05-21T05:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T13:32:54.000Z","uid":56716,"like":124,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"bb14983f4eb8c6b57d5fd17bce7e5d3bc6a6e3a4","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 馬浚偉：最擔心嘉欣畀人蝦！</span></span><br />\n我識嘉欣最久，卻反而是我最擔心的一個。有次她在微博留言給我，說她大個女了，但我還是擔心，因為嘉欣太天真、太單純，很容易被人蝦！活在無綫這個受盡保護的「溫室」當然ＯＫ，但如果要出外打拚也就難說得很。當年我看着嘉欣入行，有日我倆吃飯時叮囑她，學甚麼也好，千萬不要學壞，不要做些「不乾淨」的事，要保持純潔的內心。嘉欣一直都能做到，而且演戲上進步不少，我很欣慰。可能是我慣了對家中的親姊妹也是如此照顧吧，我的話或許有點老土、有些老竇feel，但也慶幸找到三個跟我互相尊重又愛護的妹妹呢！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20120409/00282_007.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20120409%2F00282_007.html&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e62ef67b\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20120409/00282_007.html</a>"},{"pid":"6f999e8e0e353b24c508187ec69fb179b8bd1b9e","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:02:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 馬浚偉攬郭羨妮冰釋前嫌</span></span><br />\n馬浚偉昨日更公然攬着郭羨妮合照，問到會否怕再傳緋聞，二人表示現時是很好的朋友，不諱言於新加坡工作時細談往事，將十年前的誤會一小時內說清楚，Sonija承認當時受人唆擺才產生誤會，幸而現已冰釋前嫌，馬浚偉說：「講真，嗰陣唔係有好感就做唔到好朋友，不過之後出現咗啲奇怪事，跟住一盆冷水咁！」另外，他表示一、兩年內會結婚，但還未向女友求婚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20100413/00470_050.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20100413%2F00470_050.html&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8f780e6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20100413/00470_050.html</a>"},{"pid":"c4a08786befe3cef32c8b0bb39616d1a8c8f3af1","tid":672483,"uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:03:35.000Z","msg":"吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1a575b00d7a12bbf944a00b3812ae98a4fdd13","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:04:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 馬浚偉、蔡少芬有緣無份</span></span><br />\n早前有報道指郭羨妮和馬浚偉決裂，原因是不滿有人借緋聞來做宣傳，並指馬浚偉其實早有前科，之前曾和蔡少芬及陳芷菁等女星傳緋聞。<br />\n<br />\n避談郭羨妮 <br />\n日前馬浚偉往台灣為無綫電視劇集《洛神》宣傳時，亮相電視節目《娛樂新聞》接受女主持黃嘉千訪問，講及他和蔡少芬的緋聞時，馬承認曾經很欣賞蔡少芬，並一度想追求對方，但因為兩人沒有緣份，所以做不成情人，只能做好朋友。當講到和郭羨妮的恩怨時，他則不願作評論。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20020919/2839627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20020919%2F2839627&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f98a064a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20020919%2F2839627&h=6dee09a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20020919/2839627</a>"},{"pid":"8d30fa7d322496c588871eb3d172578c6091ccb2","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 馬浚偉認與樂易玲緣薄</span></span><br />\n馬浚偉昨日主持電台新節目錄音，邀得曾傳不和的無綫高層樂易玲擔任首集嘉賓。問兩人是否「破冰」？馬浚偉直認說：「破咗好耐！」至於節目中可有談及過往恩怨？樂易玲笑說：「佢用『緣薄』嚟形容，講得幾優雅。」<br />\n<br />\n馬浚偉透露兩人同是教友，因出席梁乃鵬搞的飯局而破冰：「樂小姐話我以前生性，冇事冇幹唔使理我咁多，又唔知人哋呷醋喎！」樂易玲覺得現跟對方更為親近，問到會否再簽馬浚偉做無綫親生仔？她笑說：「我驚簽唔到喎！咁合作有好多方式嘅！」馬浚偉即表示若有合適的劇本願意回巢，而重提台慶拒絕跟對方合照，他即澄清當時被拉去做訪問。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/celebrity/呷醋致-不和-馬浚偉認與樂易玲緣薄-222023396.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fcelebrity%2F%E5%91%B7%E9%86%8B%E8%87%B4-%E4%B8%8D%E5%92%8C-%E9%A6%AC%E6%B5%9A%E5%81%89%E8%AA%8D%E8%88%87%E6%A8%82%E6%98%93%E7%8E%B2%E7%B7%A3%E8%96%84-222023396.html&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9b8ac2ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/celebrity/呷醋致-不和-馬浚偉認與樂易玲緣薄-222023396.html</a>"},{"pid":"fb77161ab7c0db9ac694ecab05926912dd50a0ec","tid":672483,"uid":61630,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:08:20.000Z","msg":"邊撚個"},{"pid":"9474a3b7082913fbf96966b541c4ad26894d5f94","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 馬浚偉唔知胡定欣情史：笑到我趴喺度</span></span><br />\n馬浚偉（馬仔）為電台節目《偶然．馬浚偉》宣傳，他透露節目中會邀請不同屆別的女性嘉賓，如有政界陳淑莊、蔣麗芸等，但不會講及政治話題，反而會了解她們的日常生活；當中亦有圈中好友鍾嘉欣、胡定欣及楊怡等，更笑謂毋須碌爆人情卡，大家也一口答應做嘉賓，不過為了解嘉賓也要上網搜集資料。他說：「我唔熟她們感情史，我真係唔知胡定欣同過馬國明同吳浩康拍拖，響節目度笑到我趴響度。不過一班嘉賓沒有問過我會問乜，但我會事前問過下有乜唔想講。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/512928-娛樂-馬浚偉唔知胡定欣情史：笑到我趴喺度\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F512928-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E9%A6%AC%E6%B5%9A%E5%81%89%E5%94%94%E7%9F%A5%E8%83%A1%E5%AE%9A%E6%AC%A3%E6%83%85%E5%8F%B2%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%91%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E8%B6%B4%E5%96%BA%E5%BA%A6&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3524b793\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F512928-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E9%A6%AC%E6%B5%9A%E5%81%89%E5%94%94%E7%9F%A5%E8%83%A1%E5%AE%9A%E6%AC%A3%E6%83%85%E5%8F%B2%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%91%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E8%B6%B4%E5%96%BA%E5%BA%A6&h=aacea173\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/512928-娛樂-馬浚偉唔知胡定欣情史：笑到我趴喺度</a>"},{"pid":"6364e92810ae95a54e38fa7bc68d707806fdc587","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n弘b可唔可以幫手貼查小欣嗰段，要加埋相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2647f7f3f790b2005d16742a4caf3816a535063","tid":672483,"uid":44190,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:11:46.000Z","msg":"馬浚偉進化~"},{"pid":"ce35583537e708129f8fc36ec1dea858d691e6ed","tid":672483,"uid":46195,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:12:24.000Z","msg":"你同美人到底有幾多鱔稿係手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f90fe1b60644858c439dfab6bbb777a578e234","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":120,"dislike":2,"score":118,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"查小欣：跟马浚伟去吃火锅，重点不是火锅有多好吃，而是他看到推着纸皮的伯伯在马路边掉了纸皮，没力气拾起，他马上跳下车帮伯伯，我想拍照，他说不,但系好人好事当然要登。（替他身后的伯伯绑穏纸皮后，他阻止我拍照）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/132720_b214b263764dc41a4ef9f6bf64a65209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F132720_b214b263764dc41a4ef9f6bf64a65209.jpg&h=d42b573a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"446c63e5a390ee2402a79d10b13ffe3023af55bf","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你同美人到底有幾多鱔稿係手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n醉曖馬囝"},{"pid":"ff7dab6512b98aee590b7518c345a5c421c7c222","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他不是黎明</span></span><br />\n馬浚偉在1993年的「第3屆先鋒歌唱比賽」中獲得冠軍後成為歌手，可惜他的宣傳口號「他不是黎明，他不是張學友」使他出道初期受到抨擊，形象變得負面，更不獲唱片公司續約，歌途不順，反而推使他涉足戲劇界，拍下不少膾炙人口的電視劇。2013年（即20年後），馬浚偉再戰樂壇，以「二牛」的名義參與新歌《給媽媽的「倦」》的詞曲創作。"},{"pid":"f2aca65ac8d478d7a14ec924b884d695d5557a5d","tid":672483,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"大廚出馬"},{"pid":"07de3fff14584c9d8df197dd020c5f9c0bd605c5","tid":672483,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8f90fe1b60644858c439dfab6bbb777a578e234","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":120,"dislike":2,"score":118,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"查小欣：跟马浚伟去吃火锅，重点不是火锅有多好吃，而是他看到推着纸皮的伯伯在马路边掉了纸皮，没力气拾起，他马上跳下车帮伯伯，我想拍照，他说不,但系好人好事当然要登。（替他身后的伯伯绑穏纸皮后，他阻止我拍照）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/132720_b214b263764dc41a4ef9f6bf64a65209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F132720_b214b263764dc41a4ef9f6bf64a65209.jpg&h=d42b573a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"吉妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪撚影啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fefd53c5cdb6618220c8de8144a2bc7724511ea","tid":672483,"uid":7001,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8f90fe1b60644858c439dfab6bbb777a578e234","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":120,"dislike":2,"score":118,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"查小欣：跟马浚伟去吃火锅，重点不是火锅有多好吃，而是他看到推着纸皮的伯伯在马路边掉了纸皮，没力气拾起，他马上跳下车帮伯伯，我想拍照，他说不,但系好人好事当然要登。（替他身后的伯伯绑穏纸皮后，他阻止我拍照）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/132720_b214b263764dc41a4ef9f6bf64a65209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F132720_b214b263764dc41a4ef9f6bf64a65209.jpg&h=d42b573a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:12:52.000Z","msg":"呢張真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83394dd468c080d5fc5501b7d1ae8f9d94852f1","tid":672483,"uid":82917,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"你開左了原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瘋狂地推呀笑撚死我！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5b9097945aecdc11caaa0c46c4308ddc24e201","tid":672483,"uid":82917,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"馬仔話演員每晚表現都會唔同，即使佢有經驗都試過入唔到戲，基督徒嘅佢自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：「我有試過一、兩日入唔到戲，舞台一出虎度門冇上到，嗰次內地演出，唔知點解總係投入唔到，好彩中場休息後先入番戲。我於是幫自己搵咗一個方法，迫自己徐志摩上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，每晚後台stand by時，我都會講『希望今日由頭上身上到尾』<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」馬仔除靠熟練綵排，佢話那副金框眼鏡都幫助唔少，好似「靈物」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樣，佢會排戲排到最後一周先戴上，「我一戴咗，任何人講嘢都聽唔到，自己只進入徐志摩世界，真係work。」"},{"pid":"d397074e99f043d733370c9019667ea2332278e2","tid":672483,"uid":82917,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"「經驗多咗仲想捽靚劇本，內容係關於徐志摩三段愛情故事，唔會heavy，仲有笑位。我演徐志摩仲想咬入深啲層次，將佢內心嘅澎湃嘭嘭聲放大，將文青內裏嘅獅子釋放出嚟，我仲會首次喺演藝舞台踩單車。」"},{"pid":"da807649e33d756e8faed11e5e260f53cf1dbaee","tid":672483,"uid":39215,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:18:37.000Z","msg":"其實條友又唔靚仔 又冇才能<br />\n都唔明點生存咁耐"},{"pid":"0de181e0844c02c7f7723e80b0d4240e31bfbdb4","tid":672483,"uid":82917,"like":203,"dislike":1,"score":202,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 馬浚偉日前接受本報訪問，表示前年自編自導自演的舞台劇《偶然．徐志摩》四萬字劇本，因自己不懂輸入法，唯有花七個月親手寫，寫到手抽筋<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"01733c4524775f051952ffda2f5ea4072cc5bf27","tid":672483,"uid":82917,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:19:24.000Z","msg":"馬浚偉回味有女等放學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馬浚偉昨日返回石硤尾母校廠商會中學出席分享會，希望在各方面出力回饋母校，例如音樂、戲劇等交流。馬仔憶述讀書時尚算乖仔，只偶爾被老師罰企走廊，被對面學校女同學取笑，他更笑言：「我都算係半條校草，人哋校草係文武全才，我勉強斯斯文文，做個好人，係文青男。試過有第二間學校女仔等我放學話想同我做朋友，成績唔好做唔到風頭躉唔緊要，冇人等放學就唔得啦。」"},{"pid":"cec4eb66e97cf9510e66adbb19c5dc3b8a3c28fe","tid":672483,"uid":82917,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"自編自導自演的馬浚偉在節目中說：「第一稿劇本其實長達四小時，但舞台劇有時間的規範，必需作出取捨。」最後劇本以兩小時四十五分鐘講述徐志摩一生的三段情，馬浚偉形容：「每Cut一粒字都係痛入心！」"},{"pid":"e4db698ae50e6b42983f45c8ac950372c94a2684","tid":672483,"uid":82917,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:20:32.000Z","msg":"馬浚偉透露與早前返港的鍾嘉欣及陳法拉見面：「兩個臨走之前都有同我食飯，嘉欣因為大肚，之前見佢喺社交網站上載食雪糕相鬧佢唔準食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。佢返嚟都同我傾咗好多工作上嘅嘢。（會再合作？）一定會。佢都話好多工作想做，佢都問我可唔可以幫佢安排或合作，我絕對樂意。我公司大門為佢而開，但叫佢諗清楚清楚佢仲生唔生先。（會去加拿大探佢？）睇吓有冇機會，佢生完先都未遲。」他又謂法拉在美國有很多演出機會，很替對方開心：「如果有機會我都想去睇佢演出，但我都同佢講如果有啱嘅劇本都會同佢傾，睇吓會唔會有機會喺舞台上再合作。」他更指法拉獲邀與當地紅星合作演出舞台劇，並叫法拉即使沒酬勞都要參演。"},{"pid":"73aa7cfa38e12278f6aa01caef78209e697407d5","tid":672483,"uid":23021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0de181e0844c02c7f7723e80b0d4240e31bfbdb4","tid":672483,"uid":82917,"like":203,"dislike":1,"score":202,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 馬浚偉日前接受本報訪問，表示前年自編自導自演的舞台劇《偶然．徐志摩》四萬字劇本，因自己不懂輸入法，唯有花七個月親手寫，寫到手抽筋<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:20:50.000Z","msg":"This ho siu"},{"pid":"ccd4e5f94e5de105f7dc51e7f5d8da54a27e828e","tid":672483,"uid":14333,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c8f90fe1b60644858c439dfab6bbb777a578e234","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":120,"dislike":2,"score":118,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"查小欣：跟马浚伟去吃火锅，重点不是火锅有多好吃，而是他看到推着纸皮的伯伯在马路边掉了纸皮，没力气拾起，他马上跳下车帮伯伯，我想拍照，他说不,但系好人好事当然要登。（替他身后的伯伯绑穏纸皮后，他阻止我拍照）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/132720_b214b263764dc41a4ef9f6bf64a65209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F132720_b214b263764dc41a4ef9f6bf64a65209.jpg&h=d42b573a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:20:59.000Z","msg":"跳車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0c9a10a3bb876dbc82c15b5916d3d537e5d76a","tid":672483,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8862027b4bc92f79a7a07e51420ba793ecf549ca","tid":672483,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:21:37.000Z","msg":"來源from g.honeyman 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬浚偉話一定會再同鍾嘉欣合作<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/672208?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/672208?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1dca03273728fd206d86714a9391d9767d5352ca","tid":672483,"uid":86558,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 馬浚偉日前接受本報訪問，表示前年自編自導自演的舞台劇《偶然．徐志摩》四萬字劇本，因自己不懂輸入法，唯有花七個月親手寫，寫到手抽筋<br />\n</span></blockquote><br />\n四萬字分七個月寫，平均每日二百字唔夠，會抽筋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957e081b94503b072b3a21f281e7830bfc784b08","tid":672483,"uid":171786,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他不是黎明</span></span><br />\n馬浚偉在1993年的「第3屆先鋒歌唱比賽」中獲得冠軍後成為歌手，可惜他的宣傳口號「<span style=\"color: red;\">他不是黎明，他不是張學友</span>」使他出道初期受到抨擊，形象變得負面，更不獲唱片公司續約，歌途不順，反而推使他涉足戲劇界，拍下不少膾炙人口的電視劇。2013年（即20年後），馬浚偉再戰樂壇，以「二牛」的名義參與新歌《給媽媽的「倦」》的詞曲創作。</blockquote><br />\n即話自己靚仔過黎明，唱得好過學友，果個年代咁講，抵你冇運行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e720d2073f4b999820d92009fc1d173fca50a888","tid":672483,"uid":89735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:05:04.000Z","msg":"唔好再貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇見都覺得柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c4968a680f33b8f4489ee4548b3318a80831af","tid":672483,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"俾鄰居話扮賊去嚇人啲狗個單新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb4913af6a3eee67b37fb16eb402ec6b31bda1e","tid":672483,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:32:05.000Z","msg":"點解班師奶幾鍾意馬撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51f0c79922173e6a8dc119df642a35c8174efdc","tid":672483,"uid":83125,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/164507_685ece95b5f581370c331a437361b510.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ese