親手寫，寫到手抽筋<br />\n</span></blockquote><br />\n四萬字分七個月寫，平均每日二百字唔夠，會抽筋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:08:55.000Z","msg":"公道啲講<br />\n作文都要刪刪減減<br />\n交兩千字文點要會寫三四千後改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70660f4427c8c07854d888b86d9b9edbd780206","tid":672483,"uid":71166,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c221e7557ffbd48ca2cf35ac75e4acad80bdb64","tid":672483,"uid":154684,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/90/Up_seat_4_cantonese_text.png/revision/latest?cb=20070209120012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F90%2FUp_seat_4_cantonese_text.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070209120012&h=79bc637e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:09:02.000Z","msg":"馬浚偉，本名馬志偉，暱稱馬仔，香港電視劇男演員及歌手。曾為香港無綫電視合約男藝員，馬浚偉每擔正的劇集都有不俗的收視，因此多年來都有「收視福將」之稱，尤其有「古裝劇收視之王」的稱號，<span style=\"color: red;\">擅於岀演古裝劇，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>惜至今仍未有奪得任何男主角相關獎項，</strong></span></span>近年以自由身身份回歸無綫電視拍攝劇集。 維基百科<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c51e27ca0de7a19c916d3bfb923082d54d37a23","tid":672483,"uid":154684,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d70660f4427c8c07854d888b86d9b9edbd780206","tid":672483,"uid":71166,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c221e7557ffbd48ca2cf35ac75e4acad80bdb64","tid":672483,"uid":154684,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/90/Up_seat_4_cantonese_text.png/revision/latest?cb=20070209120012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F90%2FUp_seat_4_cantonese_text.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070209120012&h=79bc637e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:09:02.000Z","msg":"馬浚偉，本名馬志偉，暱稱馬仔，香港電視劇男演員及歌手。曾為香港無綫電視合約男藝員，馬浚偉每擔正的劇集都有不俗的收視，因此多年來都有「收視福將」之稱，尤其有「古裝劇收視之王」的稱號，<span style=\"color: red;\">擅於岀演古裝劇，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>惜至今仍未有奪得任何男主角相關獎項，</strong></span></span>近年以自由身身份回歸無綫電視拍攝劇集。 維基百科<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:11:08.000Z","msg":"深宮計馬撚一定要拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930cc2bdb7b6e07a557c26a85dafb597c824f276","tid":672483,"uid":8705,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:11:24.000Z","msg":"但其實佢本身係咪好人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d7367f8ef2c9e788594712e79fba297e6856e3","tid":672483,"uid":119450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f999e8e0e353b24c508187ec69fb179b8bd1b9e","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:02:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 馬浚偉攬郭羨妮冰釋前嫌</span></span><br />\n馬浚偉昨日更公然攬着郭羨妮合照，問到會否怕再傳緋聞，二人表示現時是很好的朋友，不諱言於新加坡工作時細談往事，將十年前的誤會一小時內說清楚，Sonija承認當時受人唆擺才產生誤會，幸而現已冰釋前嫌，馬浚偉說：「講真，嗰陣唔係有好感就做唔到好朋友，不過之後出現咗啲奇怪事，跟住一盆冷水咁！」另外，他表示一、兩年內會結婚，但還未向女友求婚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20100413/00470_050.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20100413%2F00470_050.html&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8f780e6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20100413/00470_050.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"2010講結婚講到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea30785b913894f30ca6b4dc7bedceff07ca1160","tid":672483,"uid":154684,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"quote":{"pid":"13747a9b01df9984631f4edf3a16272cbd342255","tid":672483,"uid":187096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/90/Up_seat_4_cantonese_text.png/revision/latest?cb=20070209120012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F90%2FUp_seat_4_cantonese_text.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070209120012&h=79bc637e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n講還講 唔好貼圖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/23/1797451_830619560298364_1513952214_n.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140308124223\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F23%2F1797451_830619560298364_1513952214_n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140308124223&h=267dd40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/0/09/553958_838500806176906_1616308935_n.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140620103608\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F0%2F09%2F553958_838500806176906_1616308935_n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140620103608&h=cddffa68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/4/45/1982202_838503729509947_562825591_n.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140620103653\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F45%2F1982202_838503729509947_562825591_n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140620103653&