n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/180809_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F180809_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f2b10418&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0de47884c52139ebbbd7513dbc0f71d54622e2be","tid":672483,"uid":69038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c58292e80d3a7582ed160d0c414c9337c2d599a","tid":672483,"uid":6097,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:19:57.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦 深宮計做啦嘛<br />\n電視一日到黑播十幾廿個廣告<br />\n畀我哋抖下啦好嗎"},{"pid":"94b41cb50fa9c5cd84c494a30adf554f309eee8e","tid":672483,"uid":26658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8f90fe1b60644858c439dfab6bbb777a578e234","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":120,"dislike":2,"score":118,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"查小欣：跟马浚伟去吃火锅，重点不是火锅有多好吃，而是他看到推着纸皮的伯伯在马路边掉了纸皮，没力气拾起，他马上跳下车帮伯伯，我想拍照，他说不,但系好人好事当然要登。（替他身后的伯伯绑穏纸皮后，他阻止我拍照）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/132720_b214b263764dc41a4ef9f6bf64a65209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F132720_b214b263764dc41a4ef9f6bf64a65209.jpg&h=d42b573a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:26:41.000Z","msg":"Kobe fans"},{"pid":"8f3fa02915678958dea0cb397a992309fad416e7","tid":672483,"uid":76504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d1a575b00d7a12bbf944a00b3812ae98a4fdd13","tid":672483,"uid":56716,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:04:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 馬浚偉、蔡少芬有緣無份</span></span><br />\n早前有報道指郭羨妮和馬浚偉決裂，原因是不滿有人借緋聞來做宣傳，並指馬浚偉其實早有前科，之前曾和蔡少芬及陳芷菁等女星傳緋聞。<br />\n<br />\n避談郭羨妮 <br />\n日前馬浚偉往台灣為無綫電視劇集《洛神》宣傳時，亮相電視節目《娛樂新聞》接受女主持黃嘉千訪問，講及他和蔡少芬的緋聞時，馬承認曾經很欣賞蔡少芬，並一度想追求對方，但因為兩人沒有緣份，所以做不成情人，只能做好朋友。當講到和郭羨妮的恩怨時，他則不願作評論。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20020919/2839627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20020919%2F2839627&d=ng6VfQ%2BYF%2BPOkplb3O1wFp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f98a064a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20020919%2F2839627&h=6dee09a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20020919/2839627</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"屌原來20年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bec6444983f5661b0cc504bd0f8b03121161c23","tid":672483,"uid":7494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"支持吉妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c618f208fb72d6936b83814d55c72037009b3af","tid":672483,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035c896bcdfa8e10cf518a7fe4461fdd5b431433","tid":672483,"uid":115441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"其實d傳媒係咪有心玩9佢<br />\n差唔每次"},{"pid":"eaf72c21da125689fcde6316db48bc55588d63fc","tid":672483,"uid":115441,"like":1,"dislike":